      int search(E toFind)
      Finds the element in the stack and returns its location in the stack. Top of stack starts at 1.
      Parameters:
      toFind - -the object searched for
      Returns:
      -the location/index of the element in the stack. Starts at 1 from the top of the stack down. returns -1 if object isn't in the stack
